Package edu.monash.fit2099.interfaces

Interface ActionInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
Action, AttackAction, BreedingAction, DeathAction, DoNothingAction, DropItemAction, EatingAction, FeedAction, GrowingAction, KickAction, LayEggAction, MoveActorAction, PickFruitBushAction, PickFruitTreeAction, PickUpItemAction, SpitBehaviour, VendingAction, WindowSmashAction
public interface ActionInterface
This interface provides the ability to add methods to Action, without modifying code in the engine, or downcasting references in the game.
